---
title: Korma Spiced Beef Pilaf and Mango Chutney with Peas and Yoghurt
description: This Korma Spiced Beef Pilaf and Mango Chutney is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
